  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A control price for eggs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The authority has issued a special gazette notice on consumer affairs imposing a maximum retail price for eggs.",
        "Accordingly, the maximum retail price of a white egg is 43 rupees and the maximum retail price of a brown or red egg is 45 rupees and the same price is effective from yesterday (19), it is stated in the gazette announcement."
      ],
